msgstr "火焰图是一个 SVG 文件，Firefox 等网页浏览器可以轻松显示。执行完上述两条命令后，即可在浏览器中打开 `flamegraph.svg` ："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We see a big majority of time spent in what is supposed to be our main,\n"
