#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Next, try to access http://localhost:8080/crash:"
msgstr "接下来，请尝试访问 http://localhost:8080/crash ："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
