#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "and, finally, print the stack trace:"
msgstr "最后，打印堆栈跟踪："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/native-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
